MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 312

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE BARRIO OF PURIKAY, MUNICIPALITY OF LEBAK, PROVINCE OF SULTAN KUDARAT, ISLAND OF MINDANAO

Upon the recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale or settlement and reserved for school site purposes of the Purikay Central Elementary School, subject to private rights, if any there be, certain parcels of land of the public domain situated at Barrio Purikay, Municipality of Lebak, Province of Sultan Kudarat, Island of Mindanao, and which parcel of land is more particularly bounded and described as follows:

Lot 1293, Pls-504

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 1293, Pls-504, Lebak Public Land Subdivision) situated in the Bo. of Purikay, Municipality of Lebak, Province of Sultan Kudarat, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the N., along line 1-2 by Lot 979 (H-151434); on the N., E. & S., along lines 2-3-4-5-6 by Lot 1110 (H-226323), on the W., along line 6-1 by Lot 1322, all of Pls-504. Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being N. 01-48 E., 7,264.22 m. from B.L.L.M. No. 1, Pls-504, thence;

81.38 m. to point 2;

34.30 m. to point 3;

65.39 m. to point 4;

92.94 m. to point 5;

146.66 m. to point 6;

131.33 m. to point of

beginning, containing an area of SIXTEEN THOUSAND EIGHT HUNDRED THIRTY (16,830) square meters, more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by PLS Cyl. Conc. Mons. 15 x 60 cm. Bearings true. Date of Original Survey on February 28, 1957, and approved by the Director of Lands on July 17, 1957.

Lot 1322, Pls-504

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 1322, Pls-504, Lebak Public Land Subdivision) situated in the Barrio of Purikay, Municipality of Lebak, Province of Sultan Kudarat, Island of Mindanao. Bounded on the N., along line 4-1 by Lot 971, Pls-504 (H-154605); on the E., along line 1-2 by Lot 1293, Pls-504; on the S. & W., along lines 2-3-4 by Lot 972, Pls-504; all of Lebak Public Land Subdivision. Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being N. 01-48 E., 7264.22 m. from B.L.L.M. No. 1, Pls-504, thence;

131.33 m. to point 2;

194.52 m. to point 3;

123.88 m. to point 4;

197.75 m. to point of;

beginning, containing an area of TWENTY FOUR THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED EIGHTY SIX (24,986) square meters, more or less. All points referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by Pls-Cyl. Conc. Mons. 15 x 60 cm. Bearings true. Date of original survey on February 28, 1957 and approved by the Director of Lands on July 17, 1957.

The tracts of land herein reserved shall be non-alienable and shall not be subject to occupation, entry, sale, lease or other disposition until again declared alienable by proclamation of the President.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF, I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 6th day of January , in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Three.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

